Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  發令吧  阿爾撒魯
